Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millions of people live...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beneath this expansive sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they all harbor a myriad of wishes and feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those feelings sometimes touch,\N and collide with, other people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within some of those people are even deeper\N ties that surely connect them all together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so the feelings can be passed along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story full of those contacts and\N encounters is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethereal Echo, become light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden monster, enter this sealing circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewel Seed Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let it... get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to... chase after... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... please hear my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my magical... power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:19.19,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(319,87)\c&HFFD9FF&\frx30}Episode 01
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:19.19,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\c&HFFD9FF&\frx-30\pos(320,353)}Is this what you call a\N "mysterious encounter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you call a "mysterious encounter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty weird dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Takamachi Nanoha. A grade-schooler who goes\N to the Seishou Auxiliary Elementary School.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for the Takamachi family, \NI'm the youngest of three children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanoha. Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this to the table for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These two are my father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to get up all on your\N own today. That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my father, Takamachi Shiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the owner of our coffee shop in front of the train\N station, Midoriya, and the central pillar of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast will be ready any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this is my mother, Takamachi Momoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's one of the people in charge\N of all the sweets at Midoriya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's beautiful and kind, my beloved mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, and by the way, Midoriya is our coffee shop at\N the marketplace in front of the train station...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that sells various cakes, cream puffs,\N and different types of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a really popular shop for girls coming home from\N school and ladies around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Onii-chan and Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they still in the dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, Onee-chan, good morning!\NBreakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nanoha. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These two are my older brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Miyuki, let's leave it at that this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My older brother, Takamachi Kyouya-san,\N is a freshman in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having succeeded my father in his sword school,\N he's become my sister's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's continue after we're\N both back from school, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And, of course, there's my older sister, Takamachi \N Miyuki-san. She's a second year high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast sure is delicious!\N Especially these scrambled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I used tomatoes, cheese, and basil\N as toppings to really bring out the flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, take a good look. You should be happy\N for having a mother who's so good at cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Right, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our parents still act like newlyweds,\N and are always a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, your ribbon's loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my brother and sister really get along well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can really feel the love here, but behind\N everything, it feels like I'm floating apart from it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanoha! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuka-chan, Alisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nanoha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These are my friends, Alisa Bannings-chan\N and Tsukimura Suzuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've been in the same class ever since first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're attending the same cram school this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell from the research I had you do,\N the town we live in has a lot of different shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you look at what people actually do and how\N they do it, and ask them several questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this was a very good experience for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, there's a lot of places\N and a lot of different jobs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so my question to you is, what kind\N of job would you like in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would probably be a good idea\N to start thinking about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have already pretty much decided,\N haven't you, Alisa-chan, Suzuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my family, both my father and mother\N are company managers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'll have to study hard and succeed\N them in their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the plan, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like machines and stuff, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking it'd be nice to go into engineering...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are so great...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you next in line for the Midoriya\N coffee shop your family runs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's one of my visions for the future, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like there's something else I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I can't clearly see\N what that something is yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have no special skills or\N strong points about me, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be saying that about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm sure there's something\N only you can do, Nanoha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, aren't your grades better than mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you say that you have no strong points,\N what's that say about me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't be a good as a business administrator,\N and I'm no good with normal work, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, you shouldn't be doing that! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I can do... something only I can do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't Suzuka so awesome\N during dodge ball today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shortcut to get to cram school faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the path's a little worn-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the place I saw in my dream yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... kind of like a voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember hearing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I heard it coming from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly running off like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An animal? It looks hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you ask that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we have to take it to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a hospital, a vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... is there a vet somewhere near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... umm, I think there's one somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, I'll call my house and ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its wound isn't all that deep,\N but it certainly looks pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably been on its own for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, this is a ferret, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's someone's pet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a ferret... but if it is, it's certainly unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, about this item on its collar...\N It looks like some sort of jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's looking at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha, you're being stared at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, yeah... umm... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best to let it get some rest, so why don't\N I watch over it for you three until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why don't you come and\N see how it's doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, oh no! It's time for cram school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Doctor, thank you very much!\N We'll be back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start off with the problem we solved last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look at the example at the\N top of page 47 in your textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Example one is... 39/45.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Example one is... 39/45.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the denominator and numerator are\N divisible by 3, so it then becomes 13/15.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my family runs a food business, so raising a pet\N in the house really goes against our principles...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, who knows the answer to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, why don't we go with you?\N #29, Takamachi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 3 on page 47.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5/42
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people think they have to answer and stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people think they have to answer and stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,435)}Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,435)}Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, if you don't completely approximate\N these numbers, or don't do it correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your answer will not be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you finish the problem, you shouldn't\N rest yet. Your next step would be to-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I was wondering if maybe\N we could take in Mr. Ferret...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... a ferret, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're on the subject, just what is a "ferret"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad. It's like a long rodent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were really popular as pets a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ferrets are pretty small, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what a ferret is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... it's about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd only be taking it in for a little while,\N and you put it in a cage and properly look after it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it shouldn't be much of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouya, Miyuki, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's all eat up before the food gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko, could you pass the salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan, Suzuka-chan, everyone\N said I could keep the ferret here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow after school, let's go\N and pick it up together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to send this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same voice from last night's\N dream, and this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You, who can hear my voice, please!\N Please lend me some of your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ferret's the one speaking to me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Come to where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time we have left... the danger...\N It's already too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please... let my voice reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sound again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on? What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I don't really understand what's going\N on here, but... what is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're of the proper nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you lend me some of your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proper nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come here from another world\N in search of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I may not be able to handle the\N weight of doing such a thing alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it'd be a problem for you, but... I want\N those with the proper nature to cooperate with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you! I promise I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to use the power I carry within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use my power... my magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to repay you, so please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't the time to be talking about that, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that in your hand, close your\N eyes, and focus your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then repeat what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, who has accepted this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, who has accepted this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...upon the ancient contract,\N command you to release your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... upon the ancient contract,\N command you to release your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind in the sky...\N Stars in the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wind in the sky...\N Stars in the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a resolute heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a resolute heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beats within my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising Heart, Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.45,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by, Ready, Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such great magical prowess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, and begin to picture things in your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That which allows you to use magic,\N the form of your magical staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that which will protect your body, a strong armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... asking me to do that all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go with that for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with this outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:24:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.78,0:24:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.69,0:24:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.68,0:24:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:25:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I'm Takamachi Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I was just supposed to be a\N normal third-grader, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Something about missions\N and destinies happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.53,0:25:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}...and I've become\Na magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.22,0:25:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Just what kind of fate\N is in store for my city?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.30,0:25:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}And what about the ferret\N whose name I don't yet know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.37,0:25:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Will raising him in my house\N really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.13,0:25:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Two: My Magical\N Incantation is "Lyrical"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.14,0:25:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I, Lyrical Magical,\N will do my best!
